    • Constructor Detail

      • GoGUIIntegrator

        public GoGUIIntegrator(boolean showStartupAnimation,
                       boolean mode3D,
                       int boardSize)
        Creates a GoGUIIntegrator that is capable of configuring and controlling the GO GUI.
        Parameters:
        showStartupAnimation - if true then a startup animation will be shown when the GO GUI is started.
        mode3D - if true then the stones will be shown in 3D. Otherwise a 2D representation will be used.
        boardSize - the desired initial board size.
